This topic describes how to check current VM status in Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF) Ops Manager.

For a complete guide to monitoring PCF, see [Monitoring Pivotal Cloud Foundry](../monitoring/index.html).

## <a id="interface"></a>Monitoring VMs Using the Ops Manager Interface ##

Click any product tile and select the **Status** tab to view monitoring
information.


 <%= image_tag("status-tab.png") %>

